<chapter id="cherokee">
	<title>Cherokee</title>
	<section id="cherokee.install">
		<title>Installing Cherokee</title>
	    <screen>
	    <![CDATA[
apt-get install cherokee
	    ]]>
	    </screen>
        <para>Cherokee can be configured through a web-based control panel which we can start as follows:</para>
	    <screen>
	    <![CDATA[
cherokee-admin -b
	    ]]>
	    </screen>
	    <para>cherokee script</para>
	    <screen>
	    <![CDATA[
/etc/init.d/cherokee restart
	    ]]>
	    </screen>
	</section>
